snippet.title: Kimmel's Irish Pub
snippet.description: I spend a lot of time watching movies & TV, analyzing fantasy football and drinking beer. Kimmel's Irish Pub was built so that I can share my experiences with you. Since I would much rather watch a video than read something, all of my reviews, advice and opinions have been recorded to a video.
